# Web export build artifacts — NOT in git anymore. deploy.sh rsync's them
# straight to the VPS (Caddy serves /opt/games/godot-pvp/docs/). Keeping the
# 28MB pck out of git stops the repo ballooning on every Build commit.
# (server.json source lives at repo root and stays tracked.)
docs/

# Internal working state — not for public repo.
# Exception: codexreview.md is tracked so the scheduled review-fix routine
# (remote agent, clones from GitHub) can read the outstanding P0/P1/P2 list.
# todo.md / test.md stay local-only.
.agent/*
!.agent/codexreview.md
fix-local-camera-current.patch
builds/
